column1: Some logs added red text at the bottom stating that says: "This form is to be put in the mailbox by the warden's office door when it is brought into the unit from the radio picket each morning!"
Name we coded as "Nevemnte, J" hard to distinguish
Names "Villa" and "Villa, G" likely the same person based on handwriting
"Haynes, C" has scribbles next to his name when he signs for person, but I think that's like a scribble of his initials (happens on all his rows)
Name we coded as "Bundy, I" unsure if actually "Bundy 1"
Name coded as "L" and "LU" likely the same person based on handwriting
Names "Salvidar, J" and "Salvidar, JS" likely the same person based on handwriting
